        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-02-25 15:08:14.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Do you need to restart the drools for a new logging configuration\n > for a new controller?\n\nNo restart required. Since we have the scan=true option in the parent logback.xml, it also cascades in to the included logback-controller.xml. So every 60 seconds the configuration is refreshed if there are changes and will include any new loggers.",
        "patchset_number": 2
